These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
House: farmhouse, ranch-style
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| House     | ranch-style | farmhouse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Flower   | amaryllis | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, aristoff
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Cigar       | aristoff  | swisher |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
