The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, parkour
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Cigar   | baccarat  | bolivar |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour    |

